wikipedia_page.main: Ian Dominic McInerney (born 26 January 1964) is a former professional footballer, who played for Newcastle Blue Star, Huddersfield Town, Stockport County, Rochdale (loan), Morecambe, Runcorn, Halifax Town and Leigh RMI.
